            <title>[LU-1564] test: sanity test_200d fails if run separately </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1564</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Sanity 200d fails when running separately, on virtual machine via Xperior&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is not reproducible if run whole suite using acceptance-small.sh:&lt;br/&gt;
